    "The three variants of REPOCODER are listed as follows:• REPOCODER-gpt: Represents the variant of REPOCODER with the CodeGPT model fine-tuned on original functions.",
    "• REPOCODER-t5: Signifies the variant of REPOCODER with the CodeT5 model fine-tuned on original functions.",
    "• REPOCODER-llama: Designates the variant of RE-POCODER with the CodeLlama model fine-tuned on original functions.",
    "The hyperparameters of REPOCODER used in our experiments follow its default implementation: the retrieval-generation iteration is set to 2, the window size is 20, and the slice size is 2.RAG-based Variants of TOOLGEN.",
    "In fact, RAG method is orthogonal to our tool-integrated approach."
